wdi2-NY.GDS.TOTL.CD.def: Gross domestic savings are calculated as GDP less final consumption expenditure (total consumption). Data are in current U.S. dollars.
wdi2-NY.GDS.TOTL.CD.name: Gross domestic savings
wdi2-NY.GDS.TOTL.CD.source: World Bank national accounts data, and OECD National Accounts data files.
